>INCLUDES:</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text el_class="taco-ticket-text"]\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Everything in General Admission\r\nPLUS</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text el_class="taco-ticket-text"]\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">1-Hour Early Access, Private Tent and Private Bathrooms</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text el_class="taco-ticket-text taco-ticket-red-text"]\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">VIP Rare Tequila/Mezcal Tasting Bar</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text el_class="taco-ticket-text taco-ticket-green-text"]\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Tequila Pavilion including all</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Tequila/Mezcal tastings</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_btn title="BUY TICKETS" color="danger" align="center" link="url:%23|title:Buy%20Tickets||" el_class="t-buy-tickets-btn"][vc_column_text el_class="session-note-text"]\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>Note:</strong> All Taco Vendors will have at least one $3 Taco Item - use your Taco Tickets!</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_separator color="black" el_class="session-separator"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner][vc_column_text el_class="sessions-header per-session-header session-food-main-header"]\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">DC\'S 1ST TACO FESTIVAL</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text el_class="session-descr-header food-subtitle"]\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">DC\'s Best Taquerias and Taco Trucks Come Together to</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Showcase DC\'s Best Tacos!</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner el_class="food-column-left" width="1/2"][vc_column_text el_class="session-food-title"]Event at a Glance:[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text el_class="session-food-list"]\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>20+ Taco Trucks and Taqueria Restaurants!</li>\r\n 	<li>Unlimited Craft Beer Tasting from 25 Regional Breweries/50 Craft Beers</li>\r\n 	<li>Tequila Sampling Pavilion (Mezcal too!)</li>\r\n 	<li>Margarita Bars Choice of frozen or "on the rocks")</li>\r\n 	<li>Live Entertainment - Live Music</li>\r\n 	<li>Lucha Libre Wrestlers entertaining throughout</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Hot Sauce Zone - Get Your Hot Sauce On!</strong></li>\r\n 	<li>Taco Awards: Celebrity Judges Choose Overall Best Taco and Most Creative Taco</li>\r\n 	<li>This Event is Exclusively 21+</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner el_class="food-column-right" width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="64" img_size="full" alignment="center" el_class="session-food-img"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_btn title="BUY TICKETS" color="danger" align="center" link="url:%23|title:Buy%20Tickets||" el_class="t-buy-tickets-btn"][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Main', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '56-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-03-28 12:19:13', '2017-03-28 12:19:13', '', 56, 'http://fest.dev/2017/03/28/56-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
