oo!)</li>\r\n 	<li>Margarita Bars Choice of frozen or "on the rocks")</li>\r\n 	<li>Live Entertainment - Live Music</li>\r\n 	<li>Lucha Libre Wrestlers entertaining throughout</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Hot Sauce Zone - Get Your Hot Sauce On!</strong></li>\r\n 	<li>Taco Awards: Celebrity Judges Choose Overall Best Taco and Most Creative Taco</li>\r\n 	<li>This Event is Exclusively 21+</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner el_class="food-column-right" width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="64" img_size="full" alignment="center" el_class="session-food-img"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Main', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '56-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-03-29 13:10:26', '2017-03-29 13:10:26', '', 56, 'http://fest.dev/2017/03/29/56-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
