(237, 1, '2017-03-31 11:43:35', '2017-03-31 11:43:35', '[vc_row][vc_column][vc_raw_html][/vc_raw_html][vc_column_text el_class="location_title"]LOCATION[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text el_class="location_under_title"]Capital Riverfront - The Yards ParkLot H/I - 136 N St SE, Washington DC 20303[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][map zoom="13" height="430" border="0" style="bar" lat="38.874457" lng="-77.0055973"][/map][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text el_class="location_text"]We’re coming back... much closer to DC – shuttles from Metro, plenty of Free Parking, and More! Listen to music, bask in the sun, shop from a wide array of Virginia craft and specialty foods vendors, and enjoy the Grand Commonwealth Tradition that is the Virginia Wine Festival.[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text el_class="location_ditrections_title"]Directions[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text el_class="location_text_after_directions"]From Beltway I-495 take I-66 West 12 miles to exit 52 (Centreville exit) go south two miles on Rt. 29, turn left onto Bull Run\r\nPost Office Road and follow signs to Bull Run Park.\r\n\r\nBull Run Park lies downstream from Manassas Battlefield and runs along Bull Run Creek. One of the most comprehensive parks in the area, Bull Run has just as much to offer the Civil War buff as it does the naturalist or outdoor enthusiast. Bull Run woodlands and trails offer miles of hiking and solitude and a tree-shaded camp for relaxing. In the springtime, acres of bluebells and other wildflowers bloom beside the meandering stream.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Location', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '74-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-03-31 11:43:35', '2017-03-31 11:43:35', '', 74, 'http://fest.dev/2017/03/31/74-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(238, 1, '2017-03-31 11:46:58', '2017-03-31 11:46:58', '[vc_row][vc_column][vc_raw_html][/vc_raw_html][vc_column_text el_class="vendor_sponsor_title"]\r\n<div>VENDORS/</div>\r\n<div>SPONSORS</div>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text el_class="vendor_sponsor_date_text"]Taco Beer Tequila Sponsor Form\r\nCapitalriver Front - The Yards Park Lot H/I\r\nSaturday, July 15th, 2017[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text el_class="vendor_sponsor_text_first"]To be included in all print materials and Festival marketing, complete this form by August 1st, 2016 – we will contact you directly for full payment – full payment in advance is required and is handled by Marcato Festival software.[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text el_class="vendor_sponsor_text_second"]<strong>Please note:</strong> <em>TasteUSA has taken over management and organization of this year’s 41st Annual Virginia Wine Festival® – if you would like more information on our company, feel free to contact: <strong>Charlie Adler, ph. 202-244-3700, web: <a href="https://www.tasteusa.com/" target="_blank">TasteUSA</a> or email us at charlie@virginiawinefest.comstream.</strong></em>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_btn title="Vendor Sign-Up" color="white" align="center" link="url:%20https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSc0eGciFXPfQhyv8ZcIBC4ZNHIIEvjAOew8Z-ydAROVvJ0GRw%2Fviewform|title:Vendor%20Sign-Up||" el_class="vendor_sign_up_btn"][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Vendor/Sponsor', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '79-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-03-31 11:46:58', '2017-03-31 11:46:58', '', 79, 'http://fest.dev/2017/03/31/79-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
