="text-align: center;">General Admission $45</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text el_class="taco-ticket-text"]\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">INCLUDES:</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text el_class="taco-ticket-text"]\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">5 Taco Tickets\r\n(use for $3 Tacos at each establishment or 2 Taco Tickets for 1 Margarita)</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text el_class="taco-ticket-text"]\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Access to all taco trucks and entertainment</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text el_class="taco-ticket-text"]\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Unlimited craft beer sampling</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner el_class="single-ticket-block taco-tequila-ticket" width="1/3"][vc_single_image image="68" img_size="full" alignment="center" el_class="taco-ticket-img"][vc_column_text el_class="taco-ticket-title"]\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Tequila Tasting $65</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text el_class="taco-ticket-text"]\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">INCLUDES:</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text el_class="taco-ticket-text"]\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Everything in General Admission\r\nPLUS</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text el_class="taco-ticket-text taco-ticket-green-text"]\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Tequila Pavilion including all\r\nTequila/Mezcal tastings</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text el_class="taco-ticket-text"]\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">30+ different Tequila and Mezcals</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">See List of Tequilas/Mezcals Here</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner el_class="single-ticket-block taco-vip-ticket" width="1/3"][vc_single_image image="69" img_size="full" alignment="center" el_class="taco-ticket-img"][vc_column_text el_class="taco-ticket-title"]\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">VIP Ticket $75</p>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text el_class="taco-ticket-text"]\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"