(298, 1, '2017-04-05 11:32:17', '2017-04-05 11:32:17', '[vc_row][vc_column][vc_raw_html][/vc_raw_html][vc_column_text el_class="location_title"]LOCATION[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text el_class="location_under_title"]Capital Riverfront - The Yards ParkLot H/I - 136 N St SE, Washington DC 20003[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][map zoom="13" height="430" border="0" style="bar" lat="38.874457" lng="-77.0055973"][/map][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text el_class="location_text"]Tacos..Beer..Tequila..What\'s Not to Like?!? DC\'s 1st Taco Festival arrives at The Yards Park Lot H/I - across the street from Nat\'s Park - no baseball today, so you can get right to munching &amp; sipping on your choice of 20+ Taco Trucks/Taquerias/60+ Beers/Margaritas/Tequilas/Mezcals/Hot Sauces and More!\r\n\r\n<strong>The Official Address: Capital Riverfront - The Yards ParkLot H/I - 136 N St SE, Washington DC 20003</strong>[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text el_class="location_ditrections_title"]Directions[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text el_class="location_text_after_directions"]-Metro and Parking Access: Nearby Metro Entrances: Navy Yard Metro (Green Line): New Jersey Avenue Entrance - 1101 New Jersey Avenue SE (943 feet N), Navy Yard Metro (Green Line): M Street Entrance - 55 M Street SE (1005 feet NW);\r\n\r\nNearby Public Parking: The Yards Lot F - 136 N Street SE (289 feet NW), Nats Lot C - Garage Parking - 1500 South Capitol Street SE (498 feet W), The Yards Lot L - 285 Tingey Street SE (686 feet E), THERE IS NO GUARANTEE OF PARKING AVAILABILITY..[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Location', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '74-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-04-05 11:32:17', '2017-04-05 11:32:17', '', 74, 'http://fest.dev/2017/04/05/74-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
